titles.title: Dismissing the election contest relating to the office of Representative from the Twenty-fourth Congressional District of Florida.

action.text: The House Committee on House Administration reported an original measure, H. Rept. 110-176, by Mr. Brady (PA).

calendar.text: Placed on the House Calendar, Calendar No. 69.

action.text: Mr. Brady (PA) asked unanimous consent move to discharge the Committee of the Whole House on the State of the Union.

vote.text: On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to without objection.

action.text: Motion to reconsider laid on the table Agreed to without objection.

bill.summary: 6/12/2007--Passed House without amendment. Dismisses the election contest relating to the office of Representative from the 24th congressional district of Florida.
